{"tid":1661747,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中国網易拒絕越南要求修改《陰陽師》南海地圖　當地伺服器關閉","createTime":"2019-10-18T09:54:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T11:09:51.000Z","uid":184679,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8595712fd214a193df3d7526d60baf779c494b6d","tid":1661747,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T09:54:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5da978a9c0c9dc116d9b86ba.jpg/9asD1ryMDNiyKObMF6JumIyjiem5EosM4Hrr-OB66_g?v=w1600r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5da978a9c0c9dc116d9b86ba.jpg%2F9asD1ryMDNiyKObMF6JumIyjiem5EosM4Hrr-OB66_g%3Fv%3Dw1600r16_9&h=3cf01600&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國和越南因為南海地圖引發的爭執不斷。中美合拍動畫《長毛雪寶》（Abominable）由於片中出現中國主張的南海「九段線」地圖，早前在越南遭停止放映。<br />\n<br />\n周三（16日），中國互聯網公司網易旗下的手機遊戲《陰陽師Onmyoji》宣布關閉在越南的伺服器。據報原因是越南曾要求網易，將當地伺服器中涉及南海地圖的爭議領土歸為越南所有，遭網易拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報道，《陰陽師Onmyoji》越南伺服器最近進入海國版本的月之羽姬環節。而在這次活動的「逢魔之時」地圖上，有越南玩家發現，遊戲在南海領域的分界線這點上採用的是「九段線」畫法。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，中國劃出的「九段線」深入越南和菲律賓等國的200海里專屬經濟區。北京政府認為此線之內區域均為中國版圖。報道稱，越南方面不接受《陰陽師Onmyoji》的地圖畫法的，於是要求越南伺服器官方修改遊戲地圖，遭到網易拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n《陰陽師Onmyoji》的越南Facebook帳號在16日發文稱，其伺服器於當日停止運營，原因是「遊戲中的內容違反了越南的領土主權」，對此表示遺憾，又強調「沒有更好的解決方法」，希望大家可以理解。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，《陰陽師》推出三年以來，在中國大陸以外，還有發展海外市場，在港澳台地區、日本、韓國、泰國、越南等地發行。泰國伺服器於今年3月已宣布停止運營。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/387708/%E6%8B%92%E7%B5%95%E8%B6%8A%E5%8D%97%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9-%E9%99%B0%E9%99%BD%E5%B8%AB-%E5%8D%97%E6%B5%B7%E5%9C%B0%E5%9C%96-%E7%B6%B2%E6%98%93%E9%97%9C%E9%96%89%E7%95%B6%E5%9C%B0%E4%BC%BA%E6%9C%8D%E5%99%A8</code></pre>"},{"pid":"3987ad2829615cbf58b060ff89b6f750aeeb85f4","tid":1661747,"uid":289978,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T10:12:45.000Z","msg":"支国online仲玩黎把撚"},{"pid":"b851742cfba81828c1f4e0515b9496fec54a9c63","tid":1661747,"uid":276989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T10:33:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cef969bdf0af0879217c0c7d0686e2002a67768","tid":1661747,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T10:56:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16cfe688bc946747ed026c00e83656829817459a","tid":1661747,"uid":29858,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T11:00:37.000Z","msg":"現實唔屬於自己既野 就喺隻game入面歸自己所有<br />\n好快就有電影講成個宇宙都係屬於中國既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b81f928f48e721256dc24ccd83c99fe465127d38","tid":1661747,"uid":206207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T11:03:38.000Z","msg":"重課金班友點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa059d9354fb1bf5e211ccd75d96fc9c3afd963d","tid":1661747,"uid":144885,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T11:04:35.000Z","msg":"幾年前玩過<br />\n好後悔玩咗"},{"pid":"a5fbd4d37a390e90ea4ec268084254fac3f1e5a5","tid":1661747,"uid":214192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T11:05:39.000Z","msg":"嗱，日本 越南 你地齊齊打中國，打贏左咁乜釣魚台 中南海都係你地㗎啦"},{"pid":"e85406da5326dc74ea3930ed85647c5b66fcf428","tid":1661747,"uid":26333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T11:05:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ddb0d65991b2e80f4f62d54f14454d3d4447f2b","tid":1661747,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T11:08:03.000Z","msg":"越南好波<br />\n以牙還牙"},{"pid":"670be0f1e4330593feeec4dc76e83b87052bbc59","tid":1661747,"uid":34876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T11:09:51.000Z","msg":"唔好再畫出d呀<img src=\"/assets/f